<li>DSA 864: <a href="$(HOME)/security/2005/dsa-864">ruby1.8</a> --
    Safety bypass.
<li>DSA 865: <a href="$(HOME)/security/2005/dsa-865">hylafax</a> --
    Insecure temporary files.
</ul>

